Hiwot Ayalew Yimer (Amharic; amụrụ n'abali isii nke ọnwa Machị afọ 1990) bụ onye Etiopia ọkachamara na-agba ọsọ ogologo oge nke ebe akachamara ya bụ puku  mita atọ steeplechase
Ọ nọchitere anya Etiopia na ihe omume na 2012 Summer Olympics, ma gbara nke ise.
A mụrụ ya na Gojjam, ọ bụ nwanne nwanyị nke Wude Ayalew, onye nwetara ihe nrite na 2009 World Championships in Athletics
Hiwot mere mmetụta mbụ ya na egwuregwu n'afọ 2010

Ọ gbara nke atọ n'elu puku mita ise na asọmpi ndị Etiopia wee merie asọmpi Addis Ababa Cross Country na Disemba. Ọ meghere 2011 site na mmeri na Cross Ouest-France na Le Mans, France. Na-agba ọsọ maka Commercial Bank of Ethiopia, ọ nwetara ọnọdụ nke abụọ na Jan Meda Cross Country n'afo 2011 nke mere ka ọ bụrụ onye otu mba.
Na mpụta mba ụwa mbụ ya, ọ gbara nke iri na otu na asọmpi ụmụ nwanyị na 2011 IAAF World Cross Country Championships. O sonyere na track secuitnke 2011 IAAF Diamond League ma guzobe onwe ya
Ọ gbara ọsọ puku mita ise kacha mma nke nkeji 14:49.36 nke asatọ na Bislett Games wee bịa nke asaa na Meeting Areva

Nsogbu visa pụtara na ọ bịarutere awa ole na ole tupu mmalite nke London Grand Prix, mana ọ gosipụtara onwe ya na steeplechase na nkeji 9:23.88 kachasị mma iji nweta ọnọdụ nke abụọ n'oge ikpeazụ nke Milcah Chemos Cheywa
Ọ bụ ezie na ọ tụfuru ọnọdụ na World Championships, ọ nọ na 2011 All-Africa Games wee merie ọlaọcha na steeplechase n'azụ Hyvin Jepkemoi nke Kenya, a na-ewepụ ya na akara site na nkeji nke abụọ.

Mgbe oge ịgba ọsọ ya gasịrị, ọ nwere akara nke anọ na Great Ethiopian Run 10K road race na Cross de Atapuerca. Na mbido afọ 2012, ọ pụtara dị ka onye nke abụọ n'azụ nwanne ya nwanyị na  cross country nke Elgoibar Mmeri o meriri na asọmpi mba ahụ mere ka o nweta ohere n'òtù ndị Etiopia maka 2012 London Olympics ma o jisiri ike gbaa onye nke ise na asọmpi Olympic steeplechase. Ọ rụkwara ọrụ nke ọma na 2012 IAAF Diamond League circuit, na-enwe ọkwa atọ kachasị elu na Bislett Games, Prefontaine Classic na Weltklasse Zurich meets
Na ngwụcha afọ ahụ, ọ meriri Cross de Atapuerca

O meriri n'afọ 2013 Jan Meda International iji nweta nhọpụta maka Ethiopia na 2013 IAAF World Cross Country Championships.  Na 2013 World Championship, ọ pụtara n'ọnọdụ nke anọ, na nke isii afọ abụọ ka e mesịrị na Beijing.  N'afọ 2014, ọ meriri African Championship na Puku mita atọ
